OL,4,CTop law officer goes to court to change
OL,5,Crape rule
OL,6, Scotland's top law officer is seeking a
OL,7, change in the rules on evidence which
OL,8, could allow far more prosecutions to be
OL,9, brought in rape cases.
OL,11,FIn a rare legal move, Lord Advocate
OL,12,FDorothy Bain has asked the appeal court
OL,13,Fto overturn a ruling made by five
OL,14,Fjudges in 1997.
OL,16,FThe case is being heard by a panel of
OL,17,Fseven judges.
OL,19,FAnother senior lawyer is in court
OL,20,Fopposing the move, arguing the change
OL,21,Fcould lead to wrongful convictions.
